---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../../css/services.css";
---

<Layout
  title="Electronic Systems | GeneralSoft UAE"
  description="Professional electronic systems design and development services in the UAE. We build embedded systems, IoT devices, and integrated electronic solutions for businesses."
  path="/services/electronic-systems/"
  image="/img/og-electronic.jpg"
>
  <section class="service-content" id="electronic-services">
    <div class="service-section" style="margin-top: 120px;">
      <h2 class="service-title">Electronic Systems</h2>
      <p>
        The convergence of software and hardware is creating new possibilities for businesses across the UAE. 
        At GeneralSoft, we design and develop integrated electronic systems that combine embedded software 
        with custom hardware to solve complex challenges in industrial automation, smart infrastructure, 
        and IoT applications.
      </p>
      <p>
        From sensor integration and microcontroller programming to full system design and prototyping, 
        our team brings together expertise in both software engineering and electronics to deliver 
        complete, production-ready solutions.
      </p>

      <h3>Our Electronic Systems Services</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Embedded Systems</h4>
          <p>Firmware development for microcontrollers, RTOS-based systems, and custom embedded Linux solutions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>IoT Solutions</h4>
          <p>End-to-end IoT systems including sensor networks, data collection, cloud integration, and analytics dashboards.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Industrial Automation</h4>
          <p>PLC programming, SCADA systems, and industrial control solutions for manufacturing and process industries.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Prototyping & Testing</h4>
          <p>Rapid prototyping, PCB design, and comprehensive testing services for electronic systems and devices.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Technologies We Use</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Microcontrollers: Arduino, ESP32, STM32, Raspberry Pi</li>
        <li>Communication: MQTT, LoRaWAN, BLE, Wi-Fi, Zigbee</li>
        <li>Cloud Platforms: AWS IoT, Azure IoT Hub, Google Cloud IoT</li>
        <li>Protocols: Modbus, OPC-UA, CAN Bus, I2C, SPI</li>
        <li>Tools: Altium Designer, Eagle, KiCad for PCB design</li>
      </ul>

      <!-- Projects Proof Section -->
      <div class="projects-proof">
        <h3>Proven IoT Delivery — Projects Completed</h3>
        <p>
          Our IoT portfolio includes clinical asset tracking, cloud IoT
          platforms, and connected mobile applications with real-world
          deployments.
        </p>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>Integrated Clinical ERP with IoT Asset Tracking</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Nov 2019 – Dec 2020</span>
            <span class="role">Azure Architect / PM / Tech Lead</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Integrated IoT asset tracking with Azure IoT Hub for real-time
            medical equipment monitoring in a clinical environment. Used
            LoRaWAN and BLE for device connectivity, with 5G for high-bandwidth
            data transmission. The system tracked equipment location, usage
            patterns, and maintenance schedules, sending automated notifications
            for preventive maintenance. Integrated with HoloLens (AR) for
            immersive equipment data visualization.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">Azure IoT Hub</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">LoRaWAN</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">5G</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">BLE</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">HoloLens AR</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">IoT</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>Cloud Best Practices — IoT & Big Data POCs</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Feb 2017 – Jul 2017</span>
            <span class="role">Architect / PM / Tech Lead</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Built IoT proof-of-concept systems across multiple cloud platforms
            (Azure, AWS, GCP, IBM). Implemented IoT device management via MQTT
            protocols connecting Azure IoT Hub, Facebook, and AdaFruit IO.
            Worked with both virtual and physical IoT devices for sending and
            receiving notifications. Integrated SigFox and LoRaWAN for
            low-power wide-area network connectivity. Used Raspberry Pi with LTE
            for edge computing prototypes.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">MQTT</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Azure IoT Hub</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">SigFox</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">LoRaWAN</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Raspberry Pi</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">LTE</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>Recycling App with IoT Smart Bin Integration</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Apr 2023 – Aug 2023</span>
            <span class="role">Developer</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Integrated IoT sensors with a mobile recycling application for smart
            bin connectivity. Sensors monitored bin fill levels, temperature,
            and location, transmitting data via MQTT to the cloud. The mobile
            app displayed real-time bin status and guided users to the nearest
            available recycling point.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">IoT Sensors</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">MQTT</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Flutter</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Firebase</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Smart Bins</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>IoT Deployment via CI/CD Pipeline</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Jan 2016 – Mar 2016</span>
            <span class="role">Architect & Tech Lead</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Implemented zero-touch continuous deployment for IoT device
            firmware and configuration. Built automated CI/CD pipelines using
            TFS 2015 Release Management that deployed IoT software updates
            across device fleets. The pipeline handled device provisioning,
            configuration management, and over-the-air (OTA) firmware updates.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">CI/CD</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">IoT</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">TFS 2015</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">PowerShell</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Azure</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="faq-section">

    <div class="container">
      <div class="faq-container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Common questions about our electronic systems services.</p>
        <div class="faq-list">
          <details>
            <summary>Do you handle both hardware and software design?</summary>
            <p>Yes. We provide integrated hardware and software development services, ensuring seamless communication between your electronic systems and digital platforms.</p>
          </details>
          <details>
            <summary>Can you help with IoT product development from concept to production?</summary>
            <p>Absolutely. We guide you through the entire product development lifecycle — from concept and prototyping to testing, certification, and manufacturing support.</p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact" id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="contact-content">
        <h2>Integrate Hardware with Software</h2>
        <p>Contact our team to discuss your electronic systems project and discover how we can help you build smarter solutions.</p>
        <div class="contact-info">
          <div class="contact-item">
            <div class="contact-item-icon">🌐</div><strong>Website</strong><a href="https://generalsoft.ae">generalsoft.ae</a>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <a href="/en/contact/"><div class="contact-item-icon">📧</div><strong>Contact Us</strong><br />Get in touch</a>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <div class="contact-item-icon">📍</div><strong>Location</strong><span>Ras Al Khaimah</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
